{"tid":1614711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要破壞，我們不是暴徒","createTime":"2019-10-03T01:10:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T02:01:22.000Z","uid":28435,"like":3,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a5a8b2e973e18d297c52246e6f246cb3be7cefb2","tid":1614711,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:10:11.000Z","msg":"我們只是追求民主自由 🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻"},{"pid":"3baaa280781a8b898ae1874f28ad1c55b3f282e1","tid":1614711,"uid":28435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:14:06.000Z","msg":"「當然，真正的公義還未來臨，你們或許因而心中充滿憤怒，這乃是人之常情。但我懇請你們不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考。」"},{"pid":"9d72ec61987661e65af7ca4aa27a347ab87ec602","tid":1614711,"uid":267105,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:19:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我們只是追求民主自由 🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻</blockquote><br />\n推翻埋法治咪得"},{"pid":"ae31622076b334fa8e3e864a06e0f65ce4494894","tid":1614711,"uid":28435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:20:35.000Z","msg":"「我時常提醒自己：政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。」"},{"pid":"a38eb97ad323ef2d830a993d58b79d857d39efb4","tid":1614711,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d72ec61987661e65af7ca4aa27a347ab87ec602","tid":1614711,"uid":267105,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:19:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我們只是追求民主自由 🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻</blockquote><br />\n推翻埋法治咪得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:23:05.000Z","msg":"法治唔係守法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e22dbe39d777771f9aefd332d19f886c61375db","tid":1614711,"uid":28435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:23:51.000Z","msg":"「如是者，假如我們希望社會能夠寬容地看待被論定為「暴動」的「暴徒」，理解這些無聲者的訴求，接納這些無權者的諫言，我想，我們必須警惕每一言一行，到底會更接近目標，還是距離更遠呢？」"},{"pid":"9dcfd14076bbc46699fa2b6bfae1521e5f0214c2","tid":1614711,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d72ec61987661e65af7ca4aa27a347ab87ec602","tid":1614711,"uid":2671